_header: Saint Gregory tells and so it is
_description: Written Confession Obliterated, a Narratio in the Northern Homily Cycle — 24 couplets

BodSelSup52.First Lines:
sant gregor telles & so yt ysA clerk þat dwellyd in
                    aparysch…
BodSelSup52.Last Lines:
…go þou furth & well þou beffor þi
                    contricioun hath sauyd þe
